Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.99,0:00:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful person!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the new fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,While under my roof,\Nyou will obey me no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell you to leave,\Nthen you will leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say die, then die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be no discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else\Nthat I should be aware of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for teaching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This marks\Nthe quiet beginnings of my new life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,as fiancée to Kiyoka Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,MY HAPPY MARRIAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 2\NABOUT MY HUSBAND-TO-BE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Miss Miyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,this will be your room,\Nso use it as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Young Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there're a few rumors\Ncirculating about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but he actually has a kind heart\Nand a sweet temperament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll be heading out now\Nif that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What a luxurious bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:03:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was expecting\Nmockery and insults from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I had braced myself\Nto have been kicked out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks I'm one of the gifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why arrange this marriage otherwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All Saimoris are born with abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But not me…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll confirm if either of you possess\Nthe gift of Spirit-Sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, Kaya,\Nkeep your senses sharp…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now open the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah! You stay away.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have the ability\Nto see Grotesqueries,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,then you have Spirit-Sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When you grow up,\Nyou'll have supernatural abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, my girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,SIX MONTHS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've seen\Neven more since then, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was even able to move\Na paper shiki yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazing, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course you are, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely nothing\Nlike that other silly child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Much more talented and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's spreading rumors about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gifted,\NI'm completely useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother's cherry blossom tree and I
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,are exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm unwanted, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be waking up\Nin that house anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do much\Nbut I have to find a way to be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? It smells great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Miss Yurie, g-good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning to you, Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you're already up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You only just arrived\Nand are making breakfast so early!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.\NIt was selfish to dirty this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Selfish? Now what are you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the fiancée
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of our Young Master of the house.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you know what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the extra effort\Nwasn't too much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparing meals for the household\Nis usually my responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm getting older now\Nand not moving as fast as I used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Any help I can get in the kitchen\Nis appreciated, so thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have a little bit of time\Nuntil he wakes up for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go finish up some other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be all right\Nif I leave this one to you, Miss Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you're comfortable with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurie, I am not "Young Master"\Nif others aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning to you, Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Miss Miyo prepared breakfast\Nfor you this morning, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard she's very skilled in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It made my job much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come sit beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, take a bite of the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's poisoned, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,An obvious ploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Poisoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be eating anything\Nwith unknown contents in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Have it thrown out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to try harder than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Uh… Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The first way\NI tried to prove myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,ended in a failure\Nbeyond anything I could've ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,SPECIAL ANTI-GROTESQUERIE UNIT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Special Anti-Grotesquerie Unit\Nwelcomes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you will sharpen\Nyour abilities like a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Strict training will hone your technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the Gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,These latent supernatural abilities\Nare part of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have telekinesis,\Npyrokinesis, clairvoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Or one of the many\Nother supernatural abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You should all be proud of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider them\Nmaterialized powers of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Grotesqueries have lived\Nin this country since ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Also called demons and ghosts,\Nthey've been known to harm humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Our supernatural abilities\Nare the one and only power
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that can effectively respond\Nto these ethereal threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When's the last time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we even saw Grotesqueries?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All this preparation for no actual work
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-feels like a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we must be ready\Nfor them to appear
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,at a moment's notice… Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:09:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the number of Grotesqueries\Nhave decreased over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Missions to subjugate them\Nhave decreased as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That being said,\Nwhen a great disaster actually strikes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we can expect massive damage from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect you all\Nto have strong resolve when you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The front lines may need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, I brought you\Nthe documents you were asking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, after training this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the new troops seemed real fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is today not a good day, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem kind of busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Pay attention to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me another one of your fiancées\Nwent running for the hills after seeing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-that gloomy face of yours?\N- What witticism. Now leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! So I guessed right.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Uh, I can take a hint.\NI'll just make myself busy elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master,\Nare you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it was necessary\Nto behave that way earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo worked very hard\Nto prepare your meal
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with her whole heart and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem\Nlike the type to poison anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurie's never bothered\Nto defend anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! My mind keeps wandering.\NI can't keep slacking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no surprise.\NI just arrived and I've already failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's anything\Nlike the rumors say he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be allowed to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your room is ready for you, Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use it freely going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you'll certainly be quite busy\Nwith the marriage upcoming,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have every confidence in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you'll be able to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this, Miss?\NWhere should we take this luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go store that in my sister's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, if it isn't Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a break\Nand I'll carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you being nice to the servants\Neven if they aren't my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What an admirable fellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this is where Miyo lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If she gets kicked out…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's forced\Nto start begging in the streets,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-no matter what happens to me.\N- Hey, Koji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have you move this too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll be right there, Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be something\Nthat only I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back home, Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to apologize about this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I let myself get carried away…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in your position, Lord Kudo, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't eat anything\Nprepared by someone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that I didn't know or fully trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry\Nthat I didn't consider that beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner is waiting for you.\NMiss Yurie has prepared it by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to you on my life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that it will contain no trace of poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Know that I wasn't actually\Nsuspicious of you this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply didn't want to eat food\Nmade by someone I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive my carelessness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I am terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need for you to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After every breath you take,\Nan apology follows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm sorry--\N-That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeating the apology cheapens it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, tell me. You aren't eating, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I, I didn't… but I'm not…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not make yourself anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurie has already gone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't make\Nenough for you to eat as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… it's not her fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I just didn't have an appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Miss Yurie\Nthat I didn't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.\NThis just happens sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go heat up the bath
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-for you right away.\N-I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that I've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my abilities is manipulating fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much faster than having you\Nstarting and stoking one manually.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take on unnecessary work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even heat up the bath\Nif I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In this house,\NI'm just as useless as I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry\Nfor refusing your food this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurie… will be arriving\Nlater than normal tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You… you're certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. And if you do try to poison me,\Nyou won't get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never do something so awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So there won't be any issues then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The bath is still hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Take one before the water gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say.\NThat is so kind of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even able to thank him properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Young Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there're a few rumors\Ncirculating about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but he actually has a kind heart\Nand a sweet temperament.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He even gave me\Nthe opportunity to try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fail tomorrow, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Miss Miyo?\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother's mementos\Nand pink cherry blossom kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this have happened?\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Miss Kanoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. I'm getting back\Nmy mother's mementos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo… Please!\NWe don't know what she'll do to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.\NI'll just tell Father if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say I'm surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,since you're the daughter\Nof that thieving homewrecker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the nerve\Nto accuse me of stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How wicked are you to imply such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I must have missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all that I have left of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna see your face again
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,until you've reflected\Non what you've done today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please! Don't! Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-Someone, please! Father, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- No! Father!\N- Madam, Master, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-She's just a little girl!\N-Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who do you think you are?\NKnow your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can't treat her like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hana…\N- I can do whatever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-She's punished for defying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, someone…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Again. Every night is the same…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Hana's doing these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She was fired on the spot\Nfor trying to help me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen her since.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly hope she's happy wherever she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for repairs again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-\N-Ah, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you, Miss Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yurie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's two days in a row\Nyou're up so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… yes, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be coming later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm, after yesterday morning\Nwas so eventful,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it might be best\Nfor me to get a head start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go relax in the living room
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can handle preparing breakfast\Nto make it all easier on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um, you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my! Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After the fuss he made yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to think\Nhe'd like to try your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thankful that he's going to give me\Na chance to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not feeling\Ntoo confident about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, Miss Miyo,\Nsince I'm already here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't I help you with a few things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It tastes okay,\Nbut will he like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you very much.\N- I do this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm so fast.\NI can't guarantee how it tastes though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably as good as it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not very exciting,\Nbut I'll gladly take the compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Flattery is always appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he really eat the food I made?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My cooking is nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, this is my only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, he should be waking up\Nright about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind carrying the food\Ninto the room for me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You eat as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I… Um, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The flavor is a little different\Nfrom what I'm accustomed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong now? Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:19:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How long has it been
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,since anyone complimented me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When was the last time that happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get\Na clear picture of her upbringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Her kimono is tattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She's thin and sickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, there was something substandard\Nin her day-to-day life at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands are rough like a servant's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it hard to believe\Nshe's from a reputable family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that she wasn't raised
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,as a normal daughter\Nin her prestigious family?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say so. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think she'd tell me\Nif I asked her about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I highly doubt that she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay attention to her discreetly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll investigate the Saimori family\Non my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, Young Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen you\Nso interested in one of your fiancées.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Expressing your emotions\Nis very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to drive her away now,\Ndo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If she leaves,\Nit'll be her choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the fiancées\Nthat have come here so far
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,were only interested\Nin my money and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Young Master,\NI think she suits you quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean as a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awfully confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Saimoris…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't\Nmany gifted families out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully, I won't find\Nanything unsettling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!\NThis isn't what we agreed on, Saimori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea\Nhow much she's actually worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And just who are you to try and harp at me\Nabout my own daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard enough here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Now, you promised me, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,will marry into our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She carries Usuba blood!
